data.description: !!!PRICE REDUCED $10,000!!!This Modern Ranch Home with Stylish Updates and open concept has undergone a stunning transformation. From the exterior to the interior, every detail has been addressed. The large living room features a wood-burning fireplace and the huge picture window floods the space with natural light. The remodeled kitchen boasts subway tile, granite countertops, brand-new stainless steel appliances and a kitchen island. The main level bathroom has been completely redesigned with ceramic tile, a new vanity, toilet, mirror and light fixture. The finished basement, with new carpeting, features a bonus room that could serve as a hobby space, a home office, or an additional non-conforming bedroom. Key features: Refinished hardwood floors throughout the home, All New: Interior and Exterior paint, Light Fixtures, Garage Doors and Interior Doors. Newer HVAC system and Hot Water Heater. The immense fenced backyard includes a large shed, deck, and patio, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
